    public class CoalesceLinkage
extends CoalesceObjectHistory
implements ICoalesceLinkage
    This class represents the association between two Coalesce Entities.

      • establishLinkage

        public void establishLinkage(CoalesceEntity entity1,
                             ELinkTypes linkType,
                             CoalesceEntity entity2,
                             Marking classificationMarking,
                             String modifiedBy,
                             String modifiedByIP,
                             String label,
                             Locale inputLang,
                             boolean isReadOnly)
        Sets the two entities key, name, source and version as well as the link type, classification, modified by, input language, dates created and modified and active status.
        Parameters:
        entity1 - CoalesceEntity belonging to the first entity. Provides the entity's key, name, source and version
        linkType - ELinkTypes value for the relationship type identification between the entities
        entity2 - CoalesceEntity belonging to the second entity. Provides the entity's key, name, source and version
        classificationMarking - Marking of the classification of the relationship
        modifiedBy - identification of who entered the relationship
        modifiedByIP -
        label -
        inputLang - language that the relationship was created in
        isReadOnly -
